---
title: Roasted Beet and Lentil Salad with Feta Cheese and Walnuts
description: Roasting transforms beets from crunchy to sweet and tender! It normally takes about one hour to roast beets, so we're saving you time by pre-roasting them for you. Tossed together with roasted potatoes and onions, crunchy walnuts and lentils, this hearty recipe simply can't be beet!
